description: The SPDRS&PInternational Dividend ETF seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the total return performance of the S&PInternational Dividend OpportunitiesIndexSeeks to provide exposure to the 100 highest yielding international common stocks that have passed certain investability and stability criteriaFor potential diversification, no single country or GICS sector weight can be greater than 25%, the maximum emerging markets exposure is 15%, and no stock weight can be greater than 3% in the Index
name: SPDR S&P International Dividend ETF
